OL,5,G0300 Nobody's Fool
OL,6,     FEmily Atack and Danny Dyer host a
OL,7,     Fstrategic reality quiz, with 10
OL,8,     Fstrangers arriving at a manor to
OL,9,     Fcompete for up to #100,000 in a
OL,10,     Fgame where survival depends not
OL,11,     Fonly on how clever players are,
OL,12,     Fbut how intelligent the others
OL,13,     Fthink they are. The first private
OL,14,     Fpod quiz introduces the show's
OL,15,     Fcentral tension, with money being
OL,16,     Fearned in secret, then publicly
OL,17,     Fdeclared. Exaggeration, denial and
OL,18,     Fbluffing creep in fast, leaving
OL,19,     Fthe group unsure who to trust
